Resolved by the Senate and House of Representatives:
That the General Assembly congratulates Caitlin MacLeod-Bluver of Winooski High
School on her selection as the 2025 Vermont Teacher of the Year and Jeremy DeMink of
Edmunds Middle School in Burlington and Sonya Shedd of Wolcott Elementary School
on their recognition as Distinguished Finalists, and be it further
Resolved: That the Secretary of State be directed to send a copy of this resolution to
each of these honored teachers.
